				</ukm:Metadata><Secondary><Body DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/body" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/body" NumberOfProvisions="133" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-30"><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/part/4" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/part/4" NumberOfProvisions="19" id="part-4" RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Number><Strong>PART 4</Strong></Number><Title>ELEMENTS OF AN AWARD</Title><P1group RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Title>Introduction</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23" id="regulation-23"><Pnumber>23</Pnumber><P1para><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1" id="regulation-23-1"><Pnumber>1</Pnumber><P2para><Text>This Part contains provisions about the amounts (“the elements”) under—</Text><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/a" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/a" id="regulation-23-1-a"><Pnumber>a</Pnumber><P3para><Text>section 9 (the standard allowance);</Text></P3para></P3><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/b" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/b" id="regulation-23-1-b"><Pnumber>b</Pnumber><P3para><Text>section 10 (responsibility for children and young persons);</Text></P3para></P3><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/c" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/c" id="regulation-23-1-c"><Pnumber>c</Pnumber><P3para><Text>section 11 (housing costs); and</Text></P3para></P3><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/d" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/1/d" id="regulation-23-1-d"><Pnumber>d</Pnumber><P3para><Text>section 12 (particular needs and circumstances),</Text></P3para></P3></P2para></P2><Text>of the Act that make up the maximum amount of an award of universal credit, as provided in section 8(2) of the Act.</Text><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2" id="regulation-23-2"><Pnumber>2</Pnumber><P2para><Text>The elements to be included in an award under section 12 of the Act in respect of particular needs or circumstances are—</Text><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2/a" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2/a" id="regulation-23-2-a"><Pnumber>a</Pnumber><P3para><Text><CommentaryRef Ref="key-cb5c51db781186ad387e9851bca2f075"/>... the LCWRA element (see regulations 27  <Substitution ChangeId="key-0ae4dbe22d05e502169890a1995e2e50-1775723789872" CommentaryRef="key-0ae4dbe22d05e502169890a1995e2e50">to</Substitution>  28);</Text></P3para></P3><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2/b" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2/b" id="regulation-23-2-b"><Pnumber>b</Pnumber><P3para><Text>the carer element (see regulations 29 and 30); and</Text></P3para></P3><P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2/c" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2/c" id="regulation-23-2-c"><Pnumber>c</Pnumber><P3para><Text>the childcare costs element (see regulations 31 to 35).</Text></P3para></P3></P2para></P2></P1para></P1></P1group></Part></Body></Secondary><Commentaries><Commentary id="key-cb5c51db781186ad387e9851bca2f075" Type="F"><Para><Text>Words in reg. 23(2)(a) omitted (3.4.2017) by virtue of <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/204" id="rnb8sic5-d3e50736a1310" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2017" Number="204" Title="The Employment and Support Allowance and Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments and Transitional and Savings Provisions) Regulations 2017">The Employment and Support Allowance and Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments and Transitional and Savings Provisions) Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/204)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e50736a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e50739a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/204/regulation/1" SectionRef="regulation-1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e50736a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e50742a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/204/regulation/4/3" SectionRef="regulation-4-3" Operative="true">4(3)</CitationSubRef> (with <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e50736a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e50745a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/204/schedule/2/paragraph/8" UpTo="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/204/schedule/2/paragraph/15" StartSectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-8" EndSectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-15">Sch. 2 paras. 8-15</CitationSubRef>)</Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-0ae4dbe22d05e502169890a1995e2e50" Type="F"><Para><Text>Word in <CitationSubRef id="c5dj8mis6-00006" SectionRef="regulation-23-2" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/23/2">reg. 23(2)(a)</CitationSubRef> substituted (6.4.2026 with effect in relation to assessment periods commencing on or after that date) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2025/22" id="c5dj8mis6-00007" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2025" Number="22" Title="Universal Credit Act 2025">Universal Credit Act 2025 (c. 22)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c5dj8mis6-00007" id="c5dj8mis6-00008" SectionRef="section-2-3" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2025/22/section/2/3">s. 2(3)</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c5dj8mis6-00007" id="c5dj8mis6-00009" SectionRef="schedule-1-paragraph-10" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2025/22/schedule/1/paragraph/10" Operative="true">Sch. 1 para. 10</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary></Commentaries></Legislation>